text:
Westchester Creek (Bronx): The Wehmeyer Coal Company yard on the creek's west bank, between Ferris Place and Kirk Street. In the background is the I.R.T. elevated on Westchester Avenue.

View 1: July 25, 1928
View 2: August 25, 1935

P. L. Sperr
